import React from 'react'
import "./input.css"

const Input =()=> {
  return (<>
  <label>First Name</label>
  <input className='fn'/>
  
  <label>Last Name</label>
  <input className='ln'/>

  <label>Email</label>

  <input className='email'/>

  <label>Phone</label>

  <input className='phone'/>
  <input className='password'/>
  <input className='confpass'/>
        
  </>)
}
export default Input;
